children.name: Given I am on Start Page
And I click on start button
And I click next step button
And I select reason for visit "Work, academic visit or business"
And I click next step button
And I Select intent to stay for "more than 6 months"
And I click next step button
When I select job type "Health and care professional"
And I click next step button
Then I should see "You need a visa to work in health and care"
